'''iBeacon'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]提出的“一种可以让附近手持电子设备检测到的一种新的低功耗、低成本信号传送器”的一套可用于室内定位系统的协议。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.apple.com/legal/intellectual-property/trademark/appletmlist.html |title=Apple Trademark List |date= |accessdate=2014-03-30 |archive-date=2014-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331211600/http://www.apple.com/legal/intellectual-property/trademark/appletmlist.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://meetingofideas.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/ibeacons-bible-1-0.pdf |title=iBeacon Bible |publisher=Andy Cavallini |date= |accessdate=2014-01-01 |archive-date=2014-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125011157/http://meetingofideas.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/ibeacons-bible-1-0.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.automatedhome.co.uk/apple/apple-ibeacons-explained-smart-home-occupancy-sensing-solved.html |title=Apple iBeacons Explained – Smart Home Occupancy Sensing Solved? |publisher=Automated Home |date= |accessdate=2013-12-11 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185803/http://www.automatedhome.co.uk/apple/apple-ibeacons-explained-smart-home-occupancy-sensing-solved.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=iBeacon- The game changer in InStore Navigation|url=http://technoparkliving.com/2013/12/ibeacon-the-game-changer-in-instore-navigation/|accessdate=2014-11-19|archive-date=2014-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031190330/http://technoparkliving.com/2013/12/ibeacon-the-game-changer-in-instore-navigation/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| first=| last=| coauthors=| title=Submit your iOS 7 apps today.| date=June 2013| publisher=Apple Inc| url=https://developer.apple.com/ios7/| work=| pages=| accessdate=2013-09-23| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921124003/https://developer.apple.com/ios7/| archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref> 这种技术可以使一个智能手机或其他装置在一个iBeacon基站的感应范围内执行相应的命令。<ref>{{cite web|title=Bfonics Inc.|url=http://bfonics.com/what_is_beacon.php|publisher=Bfonics.com|accessdate=10 November 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108070354/http://bfonics.com/what_is_beacon.php|archivedate=2014年11月8日}}</ref>

这是帮助智能手机确定他们大概位置或环境的一个应用程序。在一个iBeacon基站的帮助下，智能手机的软件能大概找到它和这个iBeacon基站的相对位置。iBeacon能让手机收到附近售卖商品的通知，也可以让消费者不用拿出钱包或信用卡就能在销售点的POS机上完成支付。iBeacon技术通过[[蓝牙低功耗|蓝牙低功耗]]（BLE），也就是智能蓝牙来实现。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bluetooth.org/en-us/bluetooth-brand/smart-marks-faqs|title=Bluetooth Smart Marks FAQ|publisher=Bluetooth.org|accessdate=10 November 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724115332/https://www.bluetooth.org/en-us/bluetooth-brand/smart-marks-faqs|archivedate=2015年7月24日}}</ref>

iBeacon為利用低功耗藍牙可以近距離感測的功能來傳輸通用唯一識別碼的一個app或作業系統。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://daveaddey.com/?p=1252 |title=iBeacons |publisher=Dave Addey |date=2013-09-22 |accessdate=2013-12-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203014352/http://daveaddey.com/?p=1252 |archivedate=2013-12-03 }}</ref> 这个识别码可以在网上被查找到用以确定设备的物理位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/06/19/inside-ios-7-ibeacons-enhance-apps-location-awareness-via-bluetooth-le |title=Inside iOS 7: iBeacons enhance apps' location awareness via Bluetooth LE |publisher=Forums.appleinsider.com |date=2013-06-18 |accessdate=2013-12-11 |archive-date=2013-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219075320/http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/06/19/inside-ios-7-ibeacons-enhance-apps-location-awareness-via-bluetooth-le |dead-url=no }}</ref>或者可以在设备上触发一个动作比如在社交媒体签到或者推送通知。

各种供应商创造了不同形式的iBeacon硬件设备，包括小硬币电池设备，隨身碟和蓝牙4.0通用加密狗。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://learn.adafruit.com/pibeacon-ibeacon-with-a-raspberry-pi/overview |title=Overview  piBeacon  DIY iBeacon with a Raspberry Pi  Adafruit Learning System |accessdate=2014-05-14 |archive-date=2014-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140514204151/https://learn.adafruit.com/pibeacon-ibeacon-with-a-raspberry-pi/overview |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
